overview: When Ros is positive for pregnancy, Tiar decides to go to Jakarta with friends Sakka and Dodi to look for work as well as look for relatives who are said to be rich in Jakarta to help the debt-ridden environment. They stray to Bandung and meet a young girl named Ayana who also wants to go to Jakarta. Tiar's loyalty is tested when she has to get involved in Ayana's personal problems. Meanwhile, Ros experiences events that Tiar never imagined.
title: Molulo 2: Jodohku yang Mana?
